_pdbx_database_remark.text   
;SHEET
THE SHEET PRESENTED AS *BAR* ON SHEET RECORDS BELOW IS
ACTUALLY AN EIGHT-STRANDED BETA-BARREL.  THIS IS
REPRESENTED BY A NINE-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST AND
LAST STRANDS ARE IDENTICAL.  THERE IS A SMALL STRAND BONDED
TO THE END OF STRAND 1 OF THE BARREL.  THIS SMALL STRAND
STRAND AND STRAND 1 ARE PRESENTED AS SHEET S1.
;
